    {
      "id": "PopularPost338036",
      "post_content": "I feel like the wording is really quite strange. Sure, it's clear enough, but I second guessed myself on the meaning a couple times. Basically \"so the damage is fixed at x and you pay 1 per target? Oh wait, no because it says evenly. Oh but then why...\" And so forth. Probably just my subconscious wishing it was more powerful than it actually is. That being said, good mass removal esp. against weenie decks and a good game ender in all other situations. ",
